        "timestamp": "2019-04-09 10:28:32.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nHi Steve, understood your suggestion however WorkflowAction.java class appends configuration building block at a SERVICE level whereas we will be receiving skipFlag from TOSCA file at a VNF level. Hence we need to take a decision whether or not to call \"ConfigAssignVnfBB\" or \"ConfigDeployVnfBB\" workflow at a VNF level i.e WorkflowActionBBTasks.java\nPlease refer document attached in JIRA ticket SO-1702. During our SO-CDS integration call, it is discussed and decided to go with option 2(from the document). I am open to have a call to discuss this more.",
